# =============================================================================
# VALIDATION NOTES
# =============================================================================
# The following variables are CRITICAL and will cause deployment failure if missing:
# - DJANGO_SECRET_KEY (Django cryptographic signing)
# - DATABASE_URL (PostgreSQL connection string)
# - EMAIL_HOST_USER (SMTP authentication)
# - EMAIL_HOST_PASSWORD (SMTP authentication)
# - CLOUDINARY_URL (Media file storage)
# - AFRICAS_TALKING_API_KEY (SMS/OTP functionality)
# 
# The following variables are RECOMMENDED for production:
# - SENTRY_DSN (for error tracking and monitoring)
# - GOOGLE_MAPS_API_KEY (if using location features)
# - FRONTEND_URL (for email verification links)
# 
# All other variables have sensible defaults and are optional.
# 
# SECURITY NOTES:
# - Never commit actual values to version control
# - Use strong, unique values for all keys and passwords
# - Rotate secrets regularly in production
# - Use environment-specific values for different deployments